<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>314</hymn_number>
<title>dà yàn de jiā 迦南314</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dà yàn de jiā shì zài chì bǎng shàng, xiǎo hé de jiā shì zài dà hǎi yáng,
 wàn mín de jiā, shì zài jiǎo bǎn shàng, yī shēng zǒng shì yào zhè yàng,
 mìng zhōng yǐ zhù dìng, lì shǐ zǎo jì xià,
 hái shì yào xiàng qián, zǒng bù yào jù pà, xiàng cǎo yuán bēn chí de jùn mǎ,
 bá dāo de yuán shuài, bāng zhù yuē shū yà, tā yě yī yàng bāng nǐ xún làng zi guī jiā,
 nóng mín shāng rén hé yú fū, dōu jiāng róng yào guī gěi tā.</lyrics>
</song>